      "title": "LIOC resumes fuel distribution",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Lanka Indian Oil Company (LIOC) said it has resumed its fuel distribution from today.",
        "The company said the Trincomalee terminal is operational 24 hours a day.",
        "The LIOC has suspended fuel distribution to filling stations during the last couple of days.(DSB)"
      ],
